appearances.title: U.S. House of Representatives House Tributes to Late Rep. LaMalfa : CSPAN : January 10, 2026 2:54pm-3:59pm EST
appearances.snippet: jay obernolte from california. >> thank you very much, mr. speaker. i rise with an incredibly heavy heart to honor the life of my friend, congressman doug lamalfa. doug was one of the most effective members of this chamber. he was deeply passionate about issues that affected his constituents in northern california. and as most of the members of this chamber know, we all have little silos where people come to us for advice. i always could count on doug to give me the straight scoop on anything related to water or agriculture or rural america, and that's why we elected him as the chairman of the western caucus two years ago. and he did a phenomenal job in that role. i will miss his service there. i will also miss the man that he was. he was an incredibly decent man, a man of of exceptionally high moral character. everyone that knew doug would remark on his authenticity. when you met doug, what you saw is what you got. he was a man of deep kindness, never had a cruel or unkind word for anyone. in the years that i knew him, he was a man of incredible humi
